<t tx="ekr.20131019184243.16686">When focus is in the outline pane::

    Right-arrow (expand-and-go-right)
    Left-arrow (contract-or-go-left)
    Up-arrow (goto-prev-visible) 
    Down-arrow (goto-next-visible)
    
